Attachments
precis:
Transfer to the COMMISSIONER of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES, for community
development purposes, of the administration and control of a number of
parcels of land situated in the Community of ARVIAT that contain a total
area of some 1.45 hectares, being the beds of several ponds which were
excluded from the transfer made by Order in Council P.C. 1984-1764.
